#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.78:0.2"
msgid "8. Yamakavagga "
msgstr "8. Pairs "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.78:0.3"
msgid "78. Alaṃsutta "
msgstr "78. Good Enough "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an8.78:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi … pe … "
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.2"
msgid "chahāvuso, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu alaṃ attano, alaṃ paresaṃ. "
msgstr "“Reverends, a mendicant with six qualities is good enough for themselves and others. "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.3"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.4"
msgid "Idhāvuso, bhikkhu khippanisanti ca hoti kusalesu dhammesu; "
msgstr "A mendicant is quick-witted when it comes to skillful teachings. "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.5"
msgid "sutānañca dhammānaṃ dhāraṇajātiko hoti; "
msgstr "They readily memorize the teachings they’ve heard. "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.6"
msgid "dhātānañca dhammānaṃ atthūpaparikkhitā hoti; "
msgstr "They examine the meaning of teachings they’ve memorized. "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.7"
msgid "atthamaññāya dhammamaññāya dhammānudhammappaṭipanno ca hoti; "
msgstr "Understanding the meaning and the teaching, they practice accordingly. "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.8"
msgid "kalyāṇavāco ca hoti kalyāṇavākkaraṇo, poriyā vācāya samannāgato vissaṭṭhāya anelagaḷāya atthassa viññāpaniyā; "
msgstr "They’re a good speaker. Their voice is polished, clear, articulate, and expresses the meaning. "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.9"
msgid "sandassako ca hoti samādapako samuttejako sampahaṃsako sabrahmacārīnaṃ. "
msgstr "They educate, encourage, fire up, and inspire their spiritual companions. "

msgctxt "an8.78:1.10"
msgid "Imehi kho, āvuso, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu alaṃ attano, alaṃ paresaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these six qualities is good enough for themselves and others. "

